Poor Benny. He's smitten
with you. you know?

1130
00:51:07.690 --> 00:51:09.442
No. No. no. no.
He knows the deal.

1131
00:51:09.525 --> 00:51:11.819
He knows that...
[inhales sharply]

1132
00:51:11.903 --> 00:51:14.197
