1145
00:51:40.848 --> 00:51:42.267
-[phone vibrating]
-It's just a year lease...

1146
00:51:42.350 --> 00:51:44.101
Hold on. um...

1147
00:51:44.185 --> 00:51:45.853
-My mom's calling me.
-[sighs]

1148
00:51:45.937 --> 00:51:47.105
