1158
00:52:08.626 --> 00:52:11.629
Actually. Gemma just offered
me her apartment. [chuckles]

1159
00:52:11.712 --> 00:52:13.923
It's a year-long lease.

1160
00:52:14.006 --> 00:52:15.925
Oh.

1161
