know if I'm gonna take it.

1163
00:52:20.805 --> 00:52:22.390
But if I did.

1164
00:52:22.473 --> 00:52:25.268
it-it wouldn't mean that
I'm never coming home.

1165
00:52:25.351 --> 00:52:27.854
I just...

1166
00:52:27.937 --> 00:52:30.439
I feel like maybe
I'm not done here.

1167
