I'll be just as
excited if you stay.

1196
00:53:49.435 --> 00:53:51.103
Thank you. Mom.

1197
00:53:51.187 --> 00:53:53.648
How are you doing today?

1198
00:53:53.731 --> 00:53:54.941
Today?

1199
