1204
00:54:07.662 --> 00:54:11.999
I'm-I'm good. bean. don't
beat yourself up over it.

1205
00:54:12.083 --> 00:54:14.961
I'm sure home feels like
a million miles away.

1206
00:54:15.044 --> 00:54:18.714
