1207
00:54:18.798 --> 00:54:21.968
Gemma's apartment has a
view of the Sacré-Coeur.

1208
00:54:22.051 --> 00:54:23.678
Just like in Sabrina.

1209
00:54:23.761 --> 00:54:25.054
