1210
00:54:27.056 --> 00:54:28.182
How perfect.

1211
00:54:30.184 --> 00:54:32.061
All right.

1212
00:54:32.144 --> 00:54:35.147
Well. I should probably go. Mom.

1213
00:54:37.149 --> 00:54:39.068
I love you.

1214
00:54:39.151 --> 00:54:41.320
I love you. too. bean.

1215
00:54:41.404 --> 00:54:42.822
