forgot about everyone else.

1296
00:59:21.767 --> 00:59:23.310
I did. too.

1297
00:59:24.937 --> 00:59:27.022
[quiet. emotional music playing]

1298
00:59:33.112 --> 00:59:34.655
I never wanted to
talk about Christmas

1299
